description:
SerializedBinaryFuseFilter is an XDR Struct defined as:

```text struct SerializedBinaryFuseFilter { BinaryFuseFilterType type;

// Seed used to hash input to filter ShortHashSeed inputHashSeed;

// Seed used for internal filter hash operations ShortHashSeed filterSeed; uint32 segmentLength; uint32 segementLengthMask; uint32 segmentCount; uint32 segmentCountLength; uint32 fingerprintLength; // Length in terms of element count, not bytes

// Array of uint8_t, uint16_t, or uint32_t depending on filter type opaque fingerprints<>; }; ```
